{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this small Indie, short narrative-based game, you take the role of the Grim Reaper... on an office job. Your job is to decide which people are going to live or die. Your choices will affect the world around you. Keep the chaos away or foil plots to destroy the world and rise through the ranks of Reapers all the way up to MIDDLE-MANAGEMENT, <i>wow</i>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Death and Taxes is a game in the vein of narrative-based indie titles, such as &quot;Papers, Please&quot;, &quot;Reigns&quot;, &quot;Beholder&quot; and &quot;Animal Inspector&quot;, to name a few. The consequences of your choices are yours to bear, while the mystery of your incarnation awaits revelation! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Have a.. totally normal.. office job</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Talk to your boss</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get monies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy stuff from Mortimer\u2019s Plunder Emporium(?)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decorate your desk</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do some paperwork</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pet the cat??</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stare in the mirror and talk to yourself</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don\u2019t let the existential dread set in</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">DONT LET IT SET IN (ONLY THE FATE OF HUMANKIND IS IN YOUR HANDS, IT'S 100% OK)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Listen to that one really catchy tune in the elevator</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meaningful choices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Branching storyline with multiple [SECRET] endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make-Your-Own-Grim-Reaper!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fully voiced NPCs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Original Soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Original artwork featuring watercolour graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dialogue options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade shop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Twitch integration!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166290/extras/sss_21_12_2019_profilechoosing-mti4am5r.gif?t=1731682837\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Fate's Pet","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1166290/e51171d35a5e3779af0f1b792f59d69c9c9cb7ff.jpg"},{"name":"Curious Grim","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1166290/07d3cf0191cd8005af9115d4a0f75a8a83911939.jpg"},{"name":"I Scream","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1166290/1d98b498c0b33bc3efc226d4926923e18034243c.jpg"},{"name":"Meat Your Unmaker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1166290/01c64d04447a84c1c07a19ee909c89ed17033ed4.jpg"},{"name":"Feline Fury","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1166290/e75375faaaebbf7d64176b879fdbcee809c90c60.jpg"},{"name":"The Sacrifice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1166290/43077fd51bc3f2bb947804036213d64d71a02e43.jpg"},{"name":"Make It Rain","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1166290/ad2c57e867704ac2fd12fdcaf3fa5ca5e8115913.jpg"},{"name":"Demon Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1166290/f00b7dd5b979a305a9531d95ea36ceb4ab924305.jpg"},{"name":"Rulebender","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1166290/ac4332580aa23830f91654e29788fd9ccd763839.jpg"},{"name":"Lifegi